# state.json is used to store the last ingested date, so that we can run this script daily and only fetch new data.
# /data folder will also be ignored due size of big data. Will research how to use Git LFS in the future.
# .cache/ is used by requests_cache to store cached responses, so that we don't have to hit the API every time we run the script.